<h1>Ride Booked! 🏍</h1>
<p>Hi <strong style="color:#F0F0F0;">{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>
  Your ride has been booked successfully. We're matching you with a nearby rider right now.
</p>

<hr class="divider" />

<h2>Ride Details</h2>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">📍 Pickup</span>
  <span class="info-value">{{pickupAddress}}</span>
</div>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">🏁 Drop-off</span>
  <span class="info-value">{{dropoffAddress}}</span>
</div>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">📏 Distance</span>
  <span class="info-value">{{distanceKm}} km</span>
</div>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">⏱ Est. Duration</span>
  <span class="info-value">~{{estimatedMins}} min</span>
</div>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">💳 Payment</span>
  <span class="info-value">{{paymentMethod}}</span>
</div>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">💰 Estimated Fare</span>
  <span class="info-value"><strong style="color:#FF6B00;">KES {{estimatedFare}}</strong></span>
</div>

<hr class="divider" />

<p style="text-align:center;">
  <a href="{{trackUrl}}" class="btn">Track My Ride</a>
</p>

<div class="alert">
  <strong>Tip:</strong> You can track your rider in real time from the app.
  You can also cancel for free while the ride is still Pending.
</div>
